    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Overview - Problem statement"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In current design, all WDG alarms are mapped to CPU0 NMI alarm in SMU. But the PCXI of slave core cannot be read by master core."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Due to this we cannot store the call stack information of WDG errors in Core 1 and Core 2"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Solution"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below diagram explains the solution to above problem statement where we use SMU interrupts instead of NMI for Core 1 and Core 2 CPU WDGs"
    },
    {
